{"hablante":"A","texto":"Okay, I opened it."},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"Can you click on the message?"},
{"hablante":"A","texto":"Yes, I clicked on it. It works now!"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"Great!"}
],
